TextEng: Why are you guarding this bridge?
Why are you guarding this bridge?
Text: 왜 이 다리를 지키고 있는 거야?

TextEng: I would like to cross the bridge.
Why don't you let me across before I kill you?
Text: 날 보내주는 게 좋을 거야, 안 그러면 죽여버릴 테니까.

TextEng: If me no cross, you die!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Listen, I've been invited by Wanev. If you don't let me cross you'll be punished.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 들어봐, 난 와네브의 초대를 받았어. 날 보내주지 않으면 벌 받을 거야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me be invited by Wanev-guy. You no let me cross, he hurt you.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 와네브한테 초대받았어. 너 날 안 보내주면 그가 너 혼내.

TextEng: Would 100 gold pieces change your mind?
Maybe 100 gold make you let me cross?
